Docs/admin-guide/mm/damon/usage: update for kdamond_pid and (mk|rm)_contexts

The DAMON debugfs usage document is missing descriptions for
'kdamond_pid', 'mk_contexts', and 'rm_contexts' debugfs files.  This
commit adds those.

